## ðŸ“Œ Project Overview
Perez Fashion is a family-run **alterations, tailoring, and Nigerian wedding fashion consulting business** based in Richmond, TX.  
The goal is to deploy a professional, modern website at **https://perezfashion.com**, hosted on the home server (`databin-server`), using **Next.js + TailwindCSS + Docker + Nginx/Cloudflare Tunnel**.

This AI-driven project automates scaffolding, content population, deployment, and SEO setup for the Perez Fashion brand.

---

## ðŸŽ¯ Mission
Create a production-ready, visually appealing business website that:
1. Highlights tailoring and fashion consulting services.
2. Provides an easy way for clients to **contact, book, and consult**.
3. Improves **local SEO visibility** (â€œalterations near meâ€, â€œNigerian wedding fashion consultantâ€).
4. Supports **automated updates** and future expansions (gallery, bookings, blog, CRM).

