## ðŸ§© Core Deliverables
| Component | Description | Output |
|------------|-------------|---------|
| **Website** | Next.js + Tailwind responsive layout | `/` `/services` `/consulting` `/contact` `/gallery` |
| **Contact Form** | Formspree or local API integration | Sends to `contact@perezfashion.com` |
| **Docker Setup** | Containerized build for homelab deployment | `docker-compose.yml` |
| **SEO Assets** | Metadata, JSON-LD, robots, sitemap | Automatic generation |
| **Email Integration** | Cloudflare Email Routing or Zoho Mail | Custom domain email |
| **Automation Spec** | AI agent actions + schema | `agent_spec.yaml` (optional) |

